title: Admiral Cheng Ho
description: A brightly-lit, clean vegetarian and vegan restaurant is also a specialty coffee roaster. Specials include the signature zucchini fritters with mixed veggies, raw cashew basil cream and tangy beet root relish; quinoa pancakes with vegan butterscotch sauce and raw vanilla cream and raw granola with in-house-made organic almond milk, seasonal berries and raspberry coulis. Daily soup and stew specials. Almost all dishes are gluten free.
